  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Soak the stoned dates in almond milk for at least an hour.",
    "In a small saucepan, heat ghee over medium heat. Add cumin seeds and coriander powder, stirring well until fragrant.",
    "Stir in soaked stoned dates into the ghee mixture until smooth and warm.",
    "Transfer to oven-safe dish or ramekins for baking. Bake for 15 minutes.",
    "Top with fresh herbs if using."
